{"tid":2421224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：股票印花稅主要收割外資 小股民收聲啦","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T11:46:36.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a96f176d62eb776ce4076be30097ad11f93f27dd","tid":2421224,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:09:49.000Z","msg":"消息：印花稅並非刻意針對港交所<br />\n<br />\n政府消息又指，相信股票交易印花稅加至0.13％不會影響香港股票市場的競爭力，又指港交所是香港獨市金融基建，證券交易必然在交易所進行，而印花稅措施並非刻意針對港交所。 <br />\n<br />\n消息又指，香港股市過去一段時間上升兩個台階，包括中國經濟強勁，外國機構投資者，透過香港增加對內地金融資產的配置，各類環球指數亦將A股等納入，這個趨勢將會持續，亞洲區其他地區難以和香港競爭。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380434&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8P8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=ad896140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380434</a>"},{"pid":"593bef0fc2dcdbecce5881f388c3a4f86bdc87fb","tid":2421224,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:11:26.000Z","msg":"市場會反映一切架啦，定啦"},{"pid":"7aa7660ff9c224a69b2bff42e24fa97c9bea2ca1","tid":2421224,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:15:42.000Z","msg":"割韮菜"},{"pid":"709700a04c82a57821e829ef3b1ffac5753e2b77","tid":2421224,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"//亞洲區其他地區難以和香港競爭//<br />\n<br />\n那裡來的自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亞洲區唔夠爭<br />\n咁美國夠唔夠爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"538e78847e860793f51f03a87634c4b1884c2d12","tid":2421224,"uid":13914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:20:06.000Z","msg":"第一個縮係北水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e7958560e8857e318b4aec45a138255508b554a","tid":2421224,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim